casebody.data:
Dayton Walther Corporation, Appellee, v. Industrial Commission of Ohio et al., Appellants.

[Cite as Dayton Walther Corp. v. Indus. Comm. (1990), 53 Ohio St. 3d 2.]

(No. 90-696 Submitted June 19, 1990 Decided July 25, 1990.) Dunlevey, Mahan & Furry, Gary W. Auman and Roselyn G. Ritchey, for appellee. Anthony J. Celebrezze, Jr., attorney general, and Gerald H. Waterman, for appellants.

This cause is reversed on authority of Wean Incorporated v. Indus. Comm. (1990), 52 Ohio St. 3d 266, 557 N.E. 2d 121.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
